title: How to Earn More $$$
eventShortDescription: ​This one day workshop has been designed for developers. The program is unique in that it brings together in the one forum two of Australia's leading presenters in their respective fields. Be prepared to be shocked, challenged and amazed as Steve and Adam dispel a number of myths about client interactions and what the client is really seeking from their IT provider.
